===Noun===
'''groove'''

#a [[long]], [[narrow]] [[channel]] or [[depression]]; such a [[slot]] cut into a hard material to provide a [[location]] for an [[engineering]] [[component]]
#a [[fixed]] [[routine]]
#the [[middle]] of the [[strike]] [[zone]] in [[baseball]] [[where]] a [[pitch]] is [[most]] [[easily]] [[hit]]
#a [[pronounced]], enjoyable [[rhythm]]

